What are you doing here at this hour?

685
00:55:38,565 --> 00:55:40,442
You're such an idiot, I'm out of here.

686
00:55:40,525 --> 00:55:43,987
CONGRATULATIONS ON THE OPENING
OF YOUR CLINIC, CHAIL E&amp;C CHOI MUN-DO

687
00:55:54,122 --> 00:55:57,667
Now I realize just how desperately
you want the chairman position since you

688
00:55:57,750 --> 00:55:59,627
have no issues stalking me like this.

689
00:56:03,131 --> 00:56:07,010
Still… you shouldn't have used illegal
methods.

690
00:56:07,093 --> 00:56:10,847
I'm so sorry, I shouldn't have done
what they asked me no matter how much

691
00:56:10,930 --> 00:56:14,934
money they offered. I promise to pay for
what I've done, but please, you have to

692
00:56:15,018 --> 00:56:15,852
help me.

693
00:56:21,191 --> 00:56:25,570
So what? You think you've got me by the
throat now?

694
00:56:28,323 --> 00:56:31,701
I know you sacrificed everything
for this, and I know how desperate

695
00:56:31,784 --> 00:56:34,120
you are, but… didn't you think of
Seo-jun?

696
00:57:03,733 --> 00:57:07,445
You're right. I had to put everything
on the line to get in this position.

697
00:57:07,529 --> 00:57:11,741
And you? What have you sacrificed?

698
00:57:13,826 --> 00:57:17,288
You screw up everything you touch,
and bully others with your status.

699
00:57:17,372 --> 00:57:20,375
Do you think you deserve this?

700
00:57:27,715 --> 00:57:30,760
Forget it. I'm done here.

701
00:57:52,282 --> 00:57:55,034
-What are you doing?
-I have something to show you too.

702
00:58:16,222 --> 00:58:17,223
What is this?

703
00:58:18,057 --> 00:58:21,561
Why don't you ask her yourself? What sort
of things are there for a man

704
00:58:21,644 --> 00:58:23,896
and a woman to do when they're alone
together?

705
00:58:23,980 --> 00:58:26,608
Don't be ridiculous. What kind
of business could someone like you

706
00:58:26,691 --> 00:58:30,820
have with her? You probably thought you
could blackmail me with these photos.

707
00:58:30,903 --> 00:58:34,699
You seem to really trust her. Do you
know what kind of deal she and I made?

708
00:58:40,330 --> 00:58:43,916
You seem to have made a miscalculation.
That's too bad. You think I'd get

709
00:58:44,000 --> 00:58:46,919
involved with her? Really?

710
00:58:50,048 --> 00:58:53,343
You think Uncle's gonna believe that?
He's not an idiot. He's still

711
00:58:53,426 --> 00:58:57,096
heartbroken that his only son, who was
on top of the world, flushed his

712
00:58:57,180 --> 00:59:01,100
life down the drain by getting involved
with the wrong woman. Can you imagine…

713
00:59:01,184 --> 00:59:04,896
what he'd say about this girl?

714
00:59:09,359 --> 00:59:12,945
I mean, you know better than anyone after
how Uncle treated your mother.

715
00:59:13,029 --> 00:59:14,489
You little bastard, I should…

716
00:59:16,532 --> 00:59:19,952
That's right. Never give someone
something they can use against you.

717
00:59:20,036 --> 00:59:23,623
The more things you care about,
the weaker you become.

718
00:59:24,666 --> 00:59:27,585
You drop out of the firm and I'll
forget about everything.

719
00:59:28,127 --> 00:59:31,214
And of course, I'll make sure Uncle knows
nothing about this.

720
01:00:01,661 --> 01:00:04,414
What a surprise. He said he'd be late.

721
01:00:07,458 --> 01:00:10,586
Cha Se-gye. You're already here.

722
01:00:19,220 --> 01:00:20,972
What were you doing out so late?

723
01:00:22,181 --> 01:00:23,433
I had something to do.

724
01:00:23,516 --> 01:00:25,435
GIFTING HEALTH
THROUGH CARE AFFECTION

725
01:00:26,185 --> 01:00:29,439
I've had a headache all day from the
bomb you dropped on me, but you don't

726
01:00:29,522 --> 01:00:31,983
seem to have a care in the world. How
depressing.

727
01:00:34,902 --> 01:00:36,654
No, Cha Se-gye, that's not at all…

728
01:00:36,738 --> 01:00:38,614
You just throw things out carelessly…

729
01:00:39,532 --> 01:00:42,285
and treat me like a doormat, but
here I am, once again.

730
01:00:44,454 --> 01:00:45,705
Crawling towards you.

731
01:00:45,788 --> 01:00:47,999
I never did that. That is not why--

732
01:00:48,082 --> 01:00:50,168
Is it because you don't have faith in me?

733
01:00:54,005 --> 01:00:57,383
I hoped you wouldn't keep secrets
from me, but I hear you met with Choi

734
01:00:57,467 --> 01:00:59,927
Mun-do. Why didn't you tell me?

735
01:01:00,428 --> 01:01:01,304
Oh, I was going to--

736
01:01:01,387 --> 01:01:04,348
He tells me he made a deal with you.
You should've told me.

737
01:01:04,974 --> 01:01:07,310
Whatever it was, I could've done more
for you.

738
01:01:08,811 --> 01:01:11,814
I thought I had proven myself and finally
earned your trust…

739
01:01:14,650 --> 01:01:18,154
but I guess I was wrong. What more
do I have to do? What proof do you need

740
01:01:18,237 --> 01:01:23,159
now to believe in me, and open
your heart.

741
01:01:26,412 --> 01:01:29,624
If you truly don't feel the same way
about me, then just use me.

742
01:01:30,291 --> 01:01:32,376
For you, I'll happily let myself be used.

743
01:01:46,557 --> 01:01:50,228
Okay… Now, you're acting like
yourself again.

744
01:01:52,772 --> 01:01:56,234
You said you'd be able to throw
everything away. If that's true, then

745
01:01:56,317 --> 01:01:59,904
stop trying to be nice to me, or
pretending to worry about me. You need

746
01:01:59,987 --> 01:02:05,618
to think about yourself. If you wanna be
cold with me, then do it right!

747
01:02:10,915 --> 01:02:12,834
Stop playing around with my feelings.

748
01:02:17,380 --> 01:02:24,220
Let go of me. Let go! Let go! Stop!
Let go! Let go! No!

749
01:02:58,337 --> 01:03:02,675
Because of you, I'm losing my mind.

750
01:03:13,311 --> 01:03:14,228
Whoever you are…

751
01:03:17,940 --> 01:03:19,108
wherever you came from…

752
01:03:22,153 --> 01:03:22,987
I believe you.

753
01:03:24,196 --> 01:03:25,031
What?

754
01:03:26,532 --> 01:03:28,618
Whatever you're gonna say, I believe you.

755
01:03:30,912 --> 01:03:31,996
You have to trust me.

756
01:03:36,667 --> 01:03:39,503
Forget all the assholes out there,
and just focus on me!

757
01:03:43,549 --> 01:03:44,383
Please.

758
01:04:33,933 --> 01:04:37,520
MY ROYAL NEMESIS

759
01:05:05,006 --> 01:05:06,340
We're done with our trial period?

760
01:05:06,424 --> 01:05:07,591
Let's go on a date, Cha Se-gye.

761
01:05:07,675 --> 01:05:08,509
Why now?

762
01:05:08,592 --> 01:05:10,761
I'm going to give myself freely from
now on.

763
01:05:10,845 --> 01:05:13,347
So, you're my sweet Seo-ri's new
boyfriend?

764
01:05:13,431 --> 01:05:14,265
Please forgive me.

765
01:05:14,348 --> 01:05:16,934
It looks like we're on the brink
of a regime change.

766
01:05:17,018 --> 01:05:19,020
Mr. Cha has just entered HQ.

767
01:05:19,103 --> 01:05:21,022
Do you think I'll back down without a
fight?

768
01:05:21,105 --> 01:05:22,523
Have you seen the patient in Room 12?

769
01:05:22,606 --> 01:05:24,316
Are you sure… you can handle this?

770
01:05:25,067 --> 01:05:27,319
You lured and threatened a helpless old
lady?

771
01:05:28,154 --> 01:05:30,156
Ms. Shin, you have nothing to lose.

772
01:05:30,239 --> 01:05:32,908
I hate you being involved with Choi
Mun-do in any way!

773
01:05:32,992 --> 01:05:35,244
Well, you're worse than him. You hurt me
more!

774
01:05:35,327 --> 01:05:38,080
What I want is for Se-gye's wife to
have a lot to give.

775
01:05:38,831 --> 01:05:40,916
Shin Seo-ri. Answer your damn phone!

